pinger: pinger (GTK/ncurses multiping utility)
pinger:
pinger: A cyclic multi ping utility for selected addresses using GTK/ncurses.
pinger: You simply write addresses into a configuration file and after
pinger: execution of pinger, you will see small nice window, which inform you
pinger: about current status of selected hosts and their triptimes.
pinger:
pinger: http://aa.vslib.cz/silk/projekty/pinger/index.php
